Definition: The agent requesting the procedure. Allows Practitioner and Device, since these represent the intersection between DSTU 2 and STU 3. DSTU 2 allows Organization, and STU 3 allows Patient and RelatedPerson.

Short: Practitioner or Device representing the agent requesting the procedure. Allows Practitioner and Device, since these represent the intersection between DSTU 2 and STU 3. DSTU 2 allows Organization, and STU 3 allows Patient and RelatedPerson.
